Hiya, Rex...
   We buy our welding supplies from a company called Rockmount Reasearch
and Alloys http://www.rockmountresearch.com Although we have never used
it,
they have an aluminum wire available for aluminumMIG welding. I
therefore
assume that aluminumMIG welding(using gas-argon or argon mix is
recommended)
is very feasible.  Their product is called "Neptune MIG". Check it out.
